```class Solution {
    public int integerReplacement(int n) {
        int count = 0;
        while (n > 1) {
            if ((n & 1) == 1) {
                if (n == 3 || (n & 2) == 2) {
                    n--;
                } else {
                    n++;
                }
            } else {
                n /= 2;
            }
            count++;
        }
        return count;
    }
}```
